  "body": "There's a sorting issue when compiling a multi-file project in version `2.12.2` that does not exist in version `2.12.1` on my machine.\r\n\r\nI've created a minimal hardhat project to demonstrate the difference. \r\nhttps://github.com/Korkey128k/hardhat_v2.12.2-sorting-issue/tags\r\n\r\nYou'll see under each tag that the `artifacts/build-info` `json` file has the two sources flipped.\r\nVersion `2.12.1` is correct while `2.12.2` places the library file before the main file.\r\n\r\nUsing node `v18.12.1`",
